      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is for parts or a major restoration project. The engine suffers from a heavy knock and the transmission is failing to engage properly, making it unsafe to drive in its current state. Additionally, there is significant body rust and the interior shows heavy wear and tear. This is a non-running vehicle that will require towing and extensive mechanical work to become roadworthy again.",
