      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it has been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my daily commutes and weekend getaways. If you're looking for a reliable set of wheels that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you! It's been well-loved and is looking for a great new home. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
