    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, complete with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized valve timing across the power band. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a mechanical limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced to maintain chassis integrity, and the suspension geometry remains sharp with upgraded bushings. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response are exceptional, offering the precise feedback and lateral grip expected of this iconic M-division chassis.",
